Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Nanoka belum kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah sepuluh hari.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.15,0:00:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.15,0:00:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengkhawatirkan ramalan Pendeta Shoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus menyelidiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.41,0:00:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku berangkat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.78,0:00:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu sebentar, Nona Nanoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.12,0:00:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Minumlah smoothie-mu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.67,0:00:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menjijikkan! Rasanya bikin merinding!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.59,0:00:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seluruh tubuhku seperti dihancurkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.81,0:01:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.18,0:01:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sakit?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.64,0:01:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin karena aku tidak perlu\Nmeminumnya saat berada di sisi lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.02,0:01:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasa tak enak smoothie-nya mulai kusadari.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.73,0:01:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bagus untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.36,0:01:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.95,0:01:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku malah lebih baik tanpa meminumnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.33,0:01:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shiraha!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shiraha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.79,0:01:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa, Nanoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.62,0:01:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku butuh bantuanmu lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.38,0:01:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu. Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.92,0:01:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanoka dan Shiraha berpacaran sekarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.01,0:01:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.17,0:01:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia mendatanginya\Nkarena tahu Shiraha menyukainya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.43,0:01:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sebaiknya kembali\Ndan memberi tahu yang kutemukan,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.69,0:01:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi kecelakaan di jalan perbelanjaan sepi\Nterus menggangguku.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.73,0:01:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gempa Besar Kanto terjadi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.99,0:01:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pada 1 September, pukul 11.58.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.74,0:02:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Insiden jalan ambles yang kualami saat kecil
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.16,0:02:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}juga terjadi sekitar siang hari\Ntanggal 1 September.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau ingin tahu seperti apa\Ngang perbelanjaan sepi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}di Jalan Kelima di era Taisho?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, terutama sekitar waktu\NGempa Besar Kanto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat itu, area ini sebagian besar ladang
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan tampaknya\Nbukan bagian dari Kota Tokyo, jadi…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kurasa kita harus melihat\Ncatatan sejarah lokal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada jalan perbelanjaan yang terletak
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}di dekat rel kereta barang.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.96,0:04:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jalan itu
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}benar-benar ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat Gempa Besar Kanto,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.05,0:04:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}itu benar-benar terbakar habis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rupanya ada kebakaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.43,0:04:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kebakaran besar itu… Mungkinkah itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari pinjam beberapa buku ini\Ndan membagi penelitian.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katakan apa yang ingin kau ketahui.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sangat membantu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shiraha… Aku selalu bisa mengandalkanmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.53,0:04:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sama seperti Otoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.79,0:04:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Untukmu, Nanoka.\N- Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yang traktir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:04:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau yakin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia manis sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini menyenangkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enaknya pas sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu alasannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu karena pria itu selalu dingin padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa dia tidak bisa sedikit lebih ramah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus kembali membaca.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.57,0:05:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini diterbitkan sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berbagai kesaksian
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang dihimpun oleh sejarawan lokal\Npada masa itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Tidak lama setelah gempa bumi besar,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tornado api menghancurkan\Ndistrik perbelanjaan."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Jalanan ditelan api\Ndan asap hitam tebal."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Beberapa bahkan mengaku\Nmelihat kucing raksasa
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menjulang di kabut asap."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kucing raksasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin… Apa itu Byoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kalau begitu…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}siluman apa yang kulihat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.98,0:06:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi, Nanoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih untuk kemarin, Shiraha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.07,0:06:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku membaca\Nsemua sejarah lokal Jalan Kelima.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tampak mengantuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dia bergadang?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Legenda batu kunci menarik perhatianku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.59,0:06:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Batu kunci?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.88,0:06:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Batu suci yang konon bisa mencegah gempa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang-orang saat itu percaya
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.09,0:06:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ikan lele raksasa di dalam Bumi
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akan meronta-ronta dan memicu gempa bumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka pikir para dewa\Nbisa menahan ikan lele itu
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dengan batu kunci untuk menghentikan gempa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Konon, itu batu besar\Nyang tidak bisa ditemukan bahkan setelah
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menggali selama tujuh hari tujuh malam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu terdengar seperti legenda\Nyang sangat acak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tampaknya, ada batu raksasa\Nyang dikubur di bawah Jalan Kelima juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Warga lokal menyebutnya
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"batu kunci" dan memujanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"batu kunci" dan memujanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:06:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tertulis di mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Catatan itu tidak menyebutkannya\Nsecara rinci.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi mereka bilang itu menghilang\Nsaat Gempa Besar Kanto
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan meninggalkan lubang menganga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menghilang setelah bencana itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu ada cerita biasa
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.64,0:07:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tentang segerombolan tikus yang kabur
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dari area Jalan Kelima\Ndi musim panas sebelum gempa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada serangan vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beberapa insiden dilaporkan\Ndi area Jalan Kelima.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kasusnya tak terpecahkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tampaknya, ada monster pengisap darah\Nmisterius yang muncul,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}membunuh beberapa orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku menyimpang dari topik?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini gempa bumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sering terjadi belakangan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ingat gempa cukup kuat tiga hari lalu
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang menyebabkan tanah longsor\Ndi kaki bukit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pergi memeriksanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bangunan bergaya barat yang aneh\Nberdiri di lokasi
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tempat penduduk lokal\Nmengabadikan batu kunci.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bangunan bergaya barat, katamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak ingat pernah melihatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong jangan bergerak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Mao… Itu gereja Kristen, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa ada di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira aku sudah menjelajahi kota ini\Ndari atas sampai bawah, tapi…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak ingat ada gereja seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bilang gempa bumi memicu\Ntanah longsor di kaki bukit, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Mao.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tali sucinya putus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}penghalang!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti putus saat tanah longsor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penghalang dipasang di dalam kota\Nyang sudah memiliki penghalang,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan sekarang, gereja tersembunyi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.49,0:08:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkinkah…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkinkah Byoki
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}di gereja itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bau darah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Mao.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Darah ini
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tampaknya keluar dari lantai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pasti
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mao, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tahu namaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mao, tubuhmu…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,0:09:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serahkan tubuhmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.71,0:09:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serahkan tubuhmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.35,0:10:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serahkan nyawamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayakashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Mao!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.41,0:10:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka mengisap darahku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayakashi ini mengisap\Ndarah terkutuk Byoki-ku,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi jangan mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti ada darah Byoki di dalam mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.06,0:10:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau mungkin…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kalian penjaga pelindung Byoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Darah yang mengalir dari lantai ini
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah darah Byoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:10:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian meminum darah itu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan melindungi tempat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu mungkin benar. Mereka Ayakashi Kutu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mao.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.87,0:11:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami sudah lama menunggumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kini aku yakin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau di bawah sini,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Byoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.60,0:11:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mao.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serahkan tubuhmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Mao!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Otoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mengisap semua darah dari tubuhku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya tubuhmu yang kami butuhkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pedangku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang mereka minum?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Darahku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanoka, bagaimana kau menemukanku?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pergi ke klinik
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan salah satu pasien bilang\Nkau mungkin ada di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau baik-baik saja, Otoya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pakaianku robek.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tampak baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo mundur sekarang
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}selagi perhatian mereka\Nteralihkan oleh darahku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku belum pernah melihatnya\Ndalam kondisi seburuk ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beginikah
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- caramu membuat pelindung?\N- Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak akan lama bagi mereka\Nuntuk mengikuti jejak darah di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.16,0:13:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang mungkin bukan waktunya\Nmembahas gempa bumi itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.04,0:13:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan Nanoka…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau menyelamatkan hidupku tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah reaksimu berlebihan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya saja… Aku tidak pernah mengira kau
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tipe orang yang berterima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Mao.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Kau minum itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Aku butuh istirahat.\N- Kau tidur siang?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan tanpa memaksakan diri\Nseperti hari ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia masih harus memulihkan energinya\Ndengan kodoku dari waktu ke waktu
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}atau tubuhnya akan menyerah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyerah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sudah hidup selama 900 tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tubuhnya sudah mencapai batasnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lukanya butuh waktu lebih lama\Nuntuk sembuh daripada sebelumnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:14:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, jika dia minum jus kodoku,\Ndia akan sembuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, Tuan Mao dikutuk\Noleh kodoku paling jahat, Byoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, tubuhnya seperti kodoku itu sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami akhirnya melacak Byoki itu,\Ntapi kemudian…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Di mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gereja di belakang sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka membangun gereja palsu
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.11,0:14:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}di tempat batu kunci kota ini diabadikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kemungkinan besar, Byoki itu di bawahnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Batu kunci…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.32,0:14:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu menghilang saat Gempa Besar Kanto
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan meninggalkan lubang menganga.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka datang!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang harus kita lakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua akan baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami sudah memasang pelindung.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.56,0:14:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau yakin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak bisa tidur dengan keributan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.48,0:15:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Merasa lebih baik?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa bergerak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tubuhku tidak mau bergerak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, bagaimana sekarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei. Apa yang kau lakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Nanoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Itu darahku.\N- Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayakashi Kutu mengejarku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.42,0:15:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa mengoleskannya padaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau kau memancing\Nayakashi itu menjauh dari sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah malam tiba,\Npancing mereka ke gereja itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, maksudmu…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pada saat itu, aku akan siap untuk mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau memintaku menjadi umpan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau hanya perlu terus berlari.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.03,0:15:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanoka, hanya kau yang bisa kuandalkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.65,0:15:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cuma gadis muda yang rapuh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan ikut denganmu, Nona Nanoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Otoya…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu milik Otoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana dengan ini, Otoya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, itu bisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau terbang!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanoka, teruslah berlari.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan melawan mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku takkan melawan mereka\Nwalau kau menyuruhku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menjauhlah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mata Nona Nanoka…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia dalam bahaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menjauh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Ia menembusnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.43,0:16:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seolah orang-orang di sini
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}hidup di dimensi yang berbeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.10,0:17:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak mengerti apa yang terjadi,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi mereka tak bisa\Nmenyerang orang-orang di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu… Aku tak melihat\Nayakashi yang lain lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada serangan vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beberapa insiden dilaporkan terjadi\Ndi area Jalan Kelima.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tampaknya, ada monster pengisap darah\Nmisterius yang muncul,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}membunuh beberapa orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus menghentikan mereka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Nanoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti ayakashi ini
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.82,0:17:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}berhasil keluar dari penghalang!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.76,0:17:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya dia sudah mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.89,0:17:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku. Aku akan meminjam ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:18:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Otoya! Bawa dia bersamamu dan lari!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak perlu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jimat pelindung ini
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}membuatnya tidak terlihat oleh ayakashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.87,0:18:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Mudah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Darah Tuan Mao di tubuhmu\Ntelah menarik perhatian yang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tempelkan jimat praktis itu padaku juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kulakukan,\Nkau tidak akan menjadi umpan,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan orang lain akan diserang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sungguh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanoka, hanya kau yang bisa kuandalkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Membuatku melakukan ini…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.40,0:18:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tak peduli apa yang terjadi padaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mao.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku membencimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah hampir waktunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.76,0:18:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak boleh mati sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:18:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak sampai aku menghadapi Byoki itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.39,0:19:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Nanoka, kita hampir sampai di gereja.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah misi ini selesai,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan menghajar Mao!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.57,0:19:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka mengabaikan darah Tuan Mao\Npada Nona Nanoka
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}untuk mengejar aroma darah\Nyang lebih kental.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.37,0:19:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mao?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.45,0:19:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia memakai pakaian bernoda darah itu lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mao!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Tidak apa-apa, Nona Nanoka!\N- Tapi…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Itu boneka?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.22,0:19:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}terjebak dalam penghalangku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.81,0:19:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mao!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rahang Air
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.27,0:19:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akan melahapmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pergilah, Roh Jahat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.60,0:20:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kura-kura?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.05,0:20:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu Genbu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.93,0:20:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua hal di dunia ini milik salah satu
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dari Lima Elemen Onmyodo.\NKayu, Api, Tanah, Logam, Air.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiap elemen saling memengaruhi\Ndan berinteraksi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayakashi Kutu itu adalah serangga bersayap
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.82,0:20:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}milik Elemen Api.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Genbu adalah
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}hewan roh Elemen Air.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Air memadamkan api.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.87,0:20:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan kata lain, Air mengalahkan Api.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.08,0:20:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Mao membuat pelindung air\Ndi sekitar gereja
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menggunakan garam dan kedelai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayakashi ini tidak bisa kabur.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.42,0:20:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:20:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ia melahap mereka satu per satu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.18,0:21:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gerejanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.07,0:21:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}batu kuncinya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.65,0:21:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Byoki itu ada di bawah sana!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.48,0:21:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gerejanya menghilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.69,0:22:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh. Katashiro Genbu-nya!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.07,0:22:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mantraku dikalahkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.99,0:22:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi batu kuncinya retak.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.66,0:22:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya ujungnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.45,0:22:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sisa batu besarnya terletak\Njauh di bawah tanah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.95,0:22:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak bisa mencapai Byoki itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.75,0:22:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nyaris saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.25,0:22:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimanapun, batu kunci itu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.55,0:22:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akan menghilang setelah Gempa Besar Kanto.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.34,0:22:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.22,0:22:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sadarlah, Mao!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.35,0:22:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Otoya bilang\Ntubuhnya sudah mencapai batasnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.77,0:22:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katakan dia tidak akan…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.74,0:22:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tidur!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.78,0:22:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa dia kecewa dan tertidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.03,0:22:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidur di tempat seperti ini…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.83,0:22:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bangun, Mao!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.04,0:22:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sakit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.55,0:24:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.30,0:24:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Udaranya makin panas, bukan?\N- Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.56,0:24:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Orang-orangnya tidak tembus pandang.\N- Sampai jumpa, Bibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.64,0:24:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hati-hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.39,0:24:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa mendengar suara mereka…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.65,0:24:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kota ini kembali normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.15,0:24:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}500 pesan
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.57,0:24:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}belum dibaca…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.57,0:24:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah menghilang selama sebulan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.41,0:24:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari mana saja kau selama ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.20,0:24:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sungguh minta maaf, Kakek.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.70,0:25:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Nanoka, aku membawakan smoothie-mu.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.54,0:25:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.58,0:25:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.21,0:25:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melihat wajah Mao saja\Nmembuatku merasa sangat lega.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.34,0:25:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.88,0:25:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siluman yang kulihat hari itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.18,0:25:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selanjutnya, "Kenangan Hari Itu".
